info_overview: 8 way touch panel manufactured by Hogar controls.
info_inclusion: Touch and hold any key on the panel excess 5 seconds. All indication lights blinks blue, then release, touch panel start inclusion process
info_exclusion: Touch and hold any key on the panel excess 10 seconds. All indication lights blinks blue, then release, touch panel start exclusion process
